<hw>Di"a*ry</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>lasting for one day; <as>as, a
<ex>diary</ex> fever</as>.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Diary</xex> ague.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Bacon.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
